about_me: I'm an Electrical Engineering student and a self-taught Programmer.
I started programming with C++, then after that I got interested in Python and started Web Development with python.
I'm also interested in inovative technologies like Blockchain and AI, and I'm trying to learn them more.
I'm currently in the path of becomming an ML engineer.
